judge_evaluation.prompt_template:
Prompt ID: {prompt_id}
Instruction: {instruction}

Response A:
{response_a}

Response B:
{response_b}

Provide your evaluation in the following strict JSON schema:
{
  "prompt_id": "{prompt_id}",
  "checkpoint_a": "{checkpoint_a}",
  "checkpoint_b": "{checkpoint_b}",
  "response_a_scores": {
    "instruction_following": <1-5>,
    "correctness": <1-5>,
    "clarity": <1-5>,
    "completeness": <1-5>,
    "structured_output_validity": <1-5>,
    "hallucination_risk": <1-5>
  },
  "response_b_scores": {
    "instruction_following": <1-5>,
    "correctness": <1-5>,
    "clarity": <1-5>,
    "completeness": <1-5>,
    "structured_output_validity": <1-5>,
    "hallucination_risk": <1-5>
  },
  "winner": "<A or B or Tie>",
  "justification": "<short explanation>"
}
